Interface MessageCatalog

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AndroidStrings, JavaProperties, MacStrings, YamlStrings

    public interface MessageCatalog
    Interface of a message catalog which is both readable and writable. NOTE: THIS API IS EXPERIMENTAL AND SUBJECT TO CHANGE.
